parsed.explanation: Multiple corrections were made to the XML. Structural issues were addressed by adding an <INTRO> tag for the leading text, wrapping floating descriptive text in <NOTE> tags, and moving stray punctuation inside the preceding elements. A missing <FORMAT> tag was added and another tag was changed from <VOLUME> to <NOTE> for semantic correctness. One tag, <TITLE=...>, was malformed and has been corrected to standard <TITLE>...</TITLE> syntax, including escaping an ampersand. Finally, numerous content errors, likely from OCR, were corrected. These included garbled unicode characters (e.g., `Ga\u221a\u00fc` to `Gasse`) and typos (e.g., `Eyusd.` to `Eiusd.`, `8v6` to `8vo`).
